        "facts": "<p><strong>Score Interpetation</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Score</th>\n<th>Risk Group</th>\n<th>10-year Overall Survival</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&le;1</td>\n<td>Low</td>\n<td>70%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>Intermediate</td>\n<td>50%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&ge;3</td>\n<td>High</td>\n<td>35%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><b>Useful Mnemonic - NoLash</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nodal areas</li>\n<li>LDH</li>\n<li>Age</li>\n<li>Stage</li>\n<li>Hemoglobin level</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Nodal Sites</strong></p>\n<div class=\"authorimage\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://cdn-web-img.mdcalc.com/content/flipi-nodal-site.png\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1839\" alt=\"nodal sites flipi\"></div>\n<p><strong>Staging Diagram</strong></p>\n<div class=\"authorimage\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://cdn-web-img.mdcalc.com/content/flipi-staging-diagram.png\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1839\" alt=\"Follicular Lymphoma Stages\"></div>",
